ph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/9289fff34f86209053a89b1477c40d5d.poster.avif?t=1776264854\" width=576 height=502 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/9289fff34f86209053a89b1477c40d5d.webm?t=1776264854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/9289fff34f86209053a89b1477c40d5d.mp4?t=1776264854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, you will help her in all this. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will have to help her in the battle against crime... <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/a96870cbd10e935c8b49a4c0324c466e.poster.avif?t=1776264854\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/a96870cbd10e935c8b49a4c0324c466e.webm?t=1776264854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/a96870cbd10e935c8b49a4c0324c466e.mp4?t=1776264854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In battles against overweight... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/9cde71b7c282954a5b313c87efff24e7.poster.avif?t=1776264854\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1129520/extras/9cde71b7c282954a5b313c87efff24e7.webm?t=1776264854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://share